arm/imx: fix AUTO_ZRELADDR selection

The AUTO_ZRELADDR selection for ARCH_IMX_V4_V5 and ARCH_MX5 should
really be mutually exclusive to ZBOOT_ROM just like what ARCH_IMX_V6_V7
does.

